$$
\begin{cases}
OA &amp;= (L_1 \cos \theta_1, L_1 \sin \theta_1) \\
AB &amp;= (L_2 \cos \theta_2, L_2 \sin \theta_2) \\
BC &amp;= (L_3 \cos \theta_3, L_3 \sin \theta_3) \\
OB &amp;= OA + AB \\
OC &amp;= OB + BC
\end{cases}
$$

记

$$
\begin{cases}
r_1 &amp;= OA \\
r_2 &amp;= OB \\
r_3 &amp;= OC \\
\end{cases}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
T &amp;= \frac{1}{2}{m_1}\dot r_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}{m_2}\dot r_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}{m_3}\dot r_3^2\\
&amp;= \frac{{{m_1} + {m_2} + {m_3}}}{2}L_1^2\dot \theta _1^2 + \frac{{{m_2} + {m_3}}}{2}L_2^2\dot \theta _2^2 + \frac{{{m_3}}}{2}L_3^2\dot \theta _3^2 + ({m_2} + {m_3}){L_1}{L_2}{{\dot \theta }_1}{{\dot \theta }_2}\cos \left( {{\theta _2} - {\theta _1}} \right)\\
&amp;\quad + {m_3}{L_2}{L_3}{{\dot \theta }_2}{{\dot \theta }_3}\cos \left( {{\theta _3} - {\theta _2}} \right) + {m_3}{L_1}{L_3}{{\dot \theta }_1}{{\dot \theta }_3}\cos \left( {{\theta _3} - {\theta _1}} \right)
\end{align*}
$$

代入 Lagrange 方程

$$\frac{{\rm{d}}}{{{\rm{d}}t}}\left( {\frac{{\partial L}}{{\partial {{\dot q }}}}} \right) - \frac{{\partial L}}{{\partial {q}}} = 0$$

有

$$
\begin{pmatrix}
(m_1 + m_2 + m_3)L_1^2 &amp; (m_2 + m_3)L_1L_2 &amp; m_3L_1L_3 \\
(m_2 + m_3)L_1L_2 &amp; (m_2 + m_3)L_2^2 &amp; m_3L_2L_3 \\
m_3L_1L_3 &amp; m_3L_2L_3 &amp; m_3L_3^2
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\ddot{\theta}_1 \\
\ddot{\theta}_2 \\
\ddot{\theta}_3
\end{pmatrix}+
\begin{pmatrix}
(m_1 + m_2 + m_3)gL_1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; (m_2 + m_3)gL_2 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; m_3gL_3
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\theta_1 \\
\theta_2 \\
\theta_3
\end{pmatrix}=
\begin{pmatrix}
0 \\
0 \\
0
\end{pmatrix}
$$

$$M\ddot \theta + K \theta = \vec 0$$

其中

$$
M = L
\begin{pmatrix}
4 &amp; 3 &amp; 2 \\
3 &amp; 3 &amp; 2 \\
2 &amp; 2 &amp; 2
\end{pmatrix},
\quad
K = g
\begin{pmatrix}
4 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 3 &amp; 0 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 2
\end{pmatrix}
$$

计算特征多项式得

$$
\begin{aligned}
\left| K - \lambda M \right| &amp;= \left| \begin{matrix}
4(g - \lambda L) &amp; -3\lambda L &amp; -2\lambda L \\
-3\lambda L &amp; 3(g - \lambda L) &amp; -2\lambda L \\
-2\lambda L &amp; -2\lambda L &amp; 2(g - \lambda L)
\end{matrix} \right| \\
&amp;= 24g^3 - 2\lambda^3 L^3 + 26\lambda^2 g L^2 - 72\lambda g^2 L
\end{aligned}
$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
 {\lambda _1} &amp;\approx 0.385\frac{g}{L} \\
 {\lambda _2} &amp;\approx 3.367\frac{g}{L} \\
 {\lambda _3} &amp;\approx 9.247\frac{g}{L}
\end{cases}
$$

由$\lambda = {\omega ^2}$得

$$
\begin{cases}
{\omega _1} &amp;\approx 0.621\sqrt {\frac{g}{L}} \\
{\omega _2} &amp;\approx 1.835\sqrt {\frac{g}{L}} \\
{\omega _3} &amp;\approx 3.041\sqrt {\frac{g}{L}}
\end{cases}
$$

div.data-content:
依据位置

$$
\begin{cases}
OA &= (L_1 \cos \theta_1, L_1 \sin \theta_1) \\
AB &= (L_2 \cos \theta_2, L_2 \sin \theta_2) \\
BC &= (L_3 \cos \theta_3, L_3 \sin \theta_3) \\
OB &= OA + AB \\
OC &= OB + BC
\end{cases}
$$

记

$$
\begin{cases}
r_1 &= OA \\
r_2 &= OB \\
r_3 &= OC \\
\end{cases}
$$

$$
\begin{align*}
T &= \frac{1}{2}{m_1}\dot r_1^2 + \frac{1}{2}{m_2}\dot r_2^2 + \frac{1}{2}{m_3}\dot r_3^2\\
&= \frac{{{m_1} + {m_2} + {m_3}}}{2}L_1^2\dot \theta _1^2 + \frac{{{m_2} + {m_3}}}{2}L_2^2\dot \theta _2^2 + \frac{{{m_3}}}{2}L_3^2\dot \theta _3^2 + ({m_2} + {m_3}){L_1}{L_2}{{\dot \theta }_1}{{\dot \theta }_2}\cos \left( {{\theta _2} - {\theta _1}} \right)\\
&\quad + {m_3}{L_2}{L_3}{{\dot \theta }_2}{{\dot \theta }_3}\cos \left( {{\theta _3} - {\theta _2}} \right) + {m_3}{L_1}{L_3}{{\dot \theta }_1}{{\dot \theta }_3}\cos \left( {{\theta _3} - {\theta _1}} \right)
\end{align*}
$$

代入 Lagrange 方程

$$\frac{{\rm{d}}}{{{\rm{d}}t}}\left( {\frac{{\partial L}}{{\partial {{\dot q }}}}} \right) - \frac{{\partial L}}{{\partial {q}}} = 0$$

有

$$
\begin{pmatrix}
(m_1 + m_2 + m_3)L_1^2 & (m_2 + m_3)L_1L_2 & m_3L_1L_3 \\
(m_2 + m_3)L_1L_2 & (m_2 + m_3)L_2^2 & m_3L_2L_3 \\
m_3L_1L_3 & m_3L_2L_3 & m_3L_3^2
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\ddot{\theta}_1 \\
\ddot{\theta}_2 \\
\ddot{\theta}_3
\end{pmatrix}+
\begin{pmatrix}
(m_1 + m_2 + m_3)gL_1 & 0 & 0 \\
0 & (m_2 + m_3)gL_2 & 0 \\
0 & 0 & m_3gL_3
\end{pmatrix}
\begin{pmatrix}
\theta_1 \\
\theta_2 \\
\theta_3
\end{pmatrix}=
\begin{pmatrix}
0 \\
0 \\
0
\end{pmatrix}
$$

div.data-content:
代入$L_1 = L_2 = L_3 = L, m_1 = m_2 = m, m_3 = 2m$

$$M\ddot \theta + K \theta = \vec 0$$

其中

$$
M = L
\begin{pmatrix}
4 & 3 & 2 \\
3 & 3 & 2 \\
2 & 2 & 2
\end{pmatrix},
\quad
K = g
\begin{pmatrix}
4 & 0 & 0 \\
0 & 3 & 0 \\
0 & 0 & 2
\end{pmatrix}
$$

计算特征多项式得

$$
\begin{aligned}
\left| K - \lambda M \right| &= \left| \begin{matrix}
4(g - \lambda L) & -3\lambda L & -2\lambda L \\
-3\lambda L & 3(g - \lambda L) & -2\lambda L \\
-2\lambda L & -2\lambda L & 2(g - \lambda L)
\end{matrix} \right| \\
&= 24g^3 - 2\lambda^3 L^3 + 26\lambda^2 g L^2 - 72\lambda g^2 L
\end{aligned}
$$

解得

$$
\begin{cases}
{\lambda _1} &\approx 0.385\frac{g}{L} \\
{\lambda _2} &\approx 3.367\frac{g}{L} \\
{\lambda _3} &\approx 9.247\frac{g}{L}
\end{cases}
$$

由$\lambda = {\omega ^2}$得

$$
\begin{cases}
{\omega _1} &\approx 0.621\sqrt {\frac{g}{L}} \\
{\omega _2} &\approx 1.835\sqrt {\frac{g}{L}} \\
{\omega _3} &\approx 3.041\sqrt {\frac{g}{L}}
\end{cases}
$$
